reviewText: Off the wall, sometimes cruel humor. It's quite a trip.
Absolutely loved this show, from the first season to the last.  I just wish Dan Clark (and David Armand) had done more that I could watch.

I have an all region free player from LG so I can play regions 0-9 or 0-8, great quality for disc.  Show ended appropriately I think, although it would have been nice to get maybe a longer last episode.  Treacher was great.
